0180130-taberuonna|archive-date=July 30, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n\n=== Television ===\n* ''Tokumei Tantei'', [[TV Asahi]], 2012<ref>{{cite news|url=https://mantan-web.jp/article/20121111dog00m200021000c.html|language=japanese|title=\u58c7\u871c\uff1a\u300c\u533f\u540d\u63a2\u5075\u300d\u3067\u521d\u30c9\u30e9\u30de\u51fa\u6f14\u3000\"\u871c\"\u306b\u307e\u307f\u308c\u3066\u4f53\u5f53\u305f\u308a\u6f14\u6280|work=MANTAN Web|publisher=[[Mainichi Shimbun]]|date=November 12, 2012|access-date=July 29, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180730140304/https://mantan-web.jp/article/20121111dog00m200021000c.html|archive-date=July 30, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n* ''Otenki Oneesan'', [[TV Asahi]], 2013<ref>{{cite web|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130703235127/http://www.tv-asahi.co.jp/otenki/|archive-date=July 3, 2013|language=japanese|url=http://www.tv-asahi.co.jp/otenki/|title=\u91d1\u66dc\u30ca\u30a4\u30c8\u30c9\u30e9\u30de\u300c\u304a\u5929\u6c17\u304a\u59c9\u3055\u3093\u300d|publisher=[[TV Asahi]]|date=April 12, 2013|access-date=July 29, 2018}}</ref>\n* ''[[Hanzawa Naoki]]'', [[TBS Television|TBS]], 2013<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tbs.co.jp/hanzawa_naoki/report/55.html|language=japanese|title=\u534a\u6ca2\u76f4\u6a39\u3000\u307e\u305f\u3057\u3066\u3082\u672a\u6a39\u306b\u6bb4\u3089\u308c\u308b|publisher=[[TBS Television]]|date=July 31, 2013|access-date=July 29, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180730170627/http://www.tbs.co.jp/hanzawa_naoki/report/55.html|archive-date=July 30, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n* ''[[Hanako to Anne]]'', [[NHK]], 2014<ref name=asadora />\n* ''Coffee-ya no Hitobito'', [[NHK]], 2014<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www6.nhk.or.jp/drama/pastprog/detail.html?i=coffeeya|language=japanese|title=\u30d7\u30ec\u30df\u30a2\u30e0\u30c9\u30e9\u30de\u300c\u73c8\u7432\u5c4b\u306e\u4eba\u3005\u300d|publisher=[[NHK]]|date=April 5, 2014|access-date=July 29, 2018|archive-url=https://web.