 Davis]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.allmovie.com/artist/don-davis-p135764/filmography|title=Don Davis \u2013 Movies and Filmography|publisher=allmovie.com|accessdate=March 17, 2017|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170318000556/http://www.allmovie.com/artist/don-davis-p135764/filmography|archivedate=March 18, 2017|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n|\n|\n|\n|\n| Composer\n| Also credited in ''The Animatrix'', ''Enter the Matrix'' and ''[[The Matrix Online]]''.\n|-\n| [[John Gaeta]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.allmovie.com/artist/john-gaeta-p268676/filmography|title=John Gaeta \u2013 Movies and Filmography|publisher=allmovie.com|accessdate=March 17, 2017|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170318002711/http://www.allmovie.com/artist/john-gaeta-p268676/filmography|archivedate=March 18, 2017|df=mdy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://collider.com/jupiter-ascending-synopsis/|title=The Wachowski Siblings' JUPITER ASCENDING, Starring Channing Tatum and Mila Kunis, Begins Filming; First Synopsis Released|date=April 15, 2013|publisher=collider.com|accessdate=March 17, 2017|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170318000724/http://collider.com/jupiter-ascending-synopsis/|archivedate=March 18, 2017|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n|\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n|\n| {{yes}}\n|\n| [[Visual effects supervisor]], [[VFX creative director|visual effects designer]]\n| Also credited in ''Ninja Assassin'', ''Enter the Matrix'' and ''The Matrix Comics''.\n|-\n| [[Method Studios|Dan Glass]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.allmovie.com/artist/dan-glass-p320941/filmography|title=Dan Glass \u2013 Movies and Filmography|publisher=allmovie.com|accessdate=March 17, 2017|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170318001204/http://www.allmovie.com/artist/dan-glass-p320941/filmography|archivedate=March 18, 2017|df=mdy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://cinefex.com/blog/sense8/|title=The Visual Effects of \"Sense8\" \u2013 Cinefex Blog|date=June 16, 2015|publisher=cinefex.com|accessdate=March 17, 2017|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508203730/http://cinefex.com/blog/sense8/|archivedate=May 8, 2016|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n|\n|\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| Visual effects supervisor, [[Television director|TV episode director]]\n| Directed an episode of ''Sense8''. Also credited in ''[[V for Vendetta (film)|V for Vendetta]]'', ''Ninja Assassin'' and ''Enter the Matrix''.\n|-\n| [[Michael Giacchino]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.allmovie.com/artist/michael-giacchino-p298495/filmography|title=Michael Giacchino \u2013 Movies and Filmography|publisher=allmovie.com|accessdate=March 17, 2017|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170318000720/http://www.allmovie.com/artist/michael-giacchino-p298495/filmography|archivedate=March 18, 2017|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n|\n|\n|\n|\n| {{yes}}\n|\n| {{yes}}\n|\n| Composer\n|\n|-\n| [[Grant Hill (film producer)|Grant Hill]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.allmovie.com/artist/grant-hill-p167919/filmography|title=Grant Hill \u2013 Movies and Filmography|publisher=allmovie.com|accessdate=March 17, 2017|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170318002715/http://www.allmovie.com/artist/grant-hill-p167919/filmography|archivedate=March 18, 2017|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n|\n|\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| Producer, executive producer, [[unit production manager]]\n| Also credited in ''V for Vendetta'', ''Ninja Assassin'' and ''Enter the Matrix''.\n|-\n| [[James McTeigue]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.allmovie.com/artist/james-mcteigue-p268863/filmography|title=James McTeigue \u2013 Movies and Filmography|publisher=allmovie.com|accessdate=March 17, 2017|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170317234627/http://www.allmovie.com/artist/james-mcteigue-p268863/filmography|